    <item>
      <title>Version 1.0.5</title>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 16:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>6</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.5</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
          <h2>What's New</h2>
          <ul>
              <li><b>Server-anchored trial:</b> onboarding now registers the email with our backend. The trial start timestamp comes from the server, so reinstalling or changing the system clock can no longer reset the trial. Offline onboarding still works and resyncs on next launch.</li>
          </ul>
          <h2>What's Fixed</h2>
          <ul>
              <li><b>Help / Guide re-entry:</b> opening the onboarding from the Help button or the Guide menu now skips the email page when the email is already on file. First-launch onboarding is unchanged.</li>
              <li><b>Settings window</b> is now shorter (700 → 600 pt).</li>
          </ul>
      ]]></description>
