    <item>
      <title>Version 1.0.4</title>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>5</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
          <h2>What's Fixed</h2>
          <ul>
              <li><b>Fresh install onboarding:</b> the email/paywall overlay no longer covers the onboarding flow on first launch. Onboarding runs first and collects the email on
  its final page, which starts the 3-day trial.</li>
              <li><b>Email prompt copy:</b> the fallback email screen now reads "Start Your Free Trial" / "Enter your email to begin 3 days of full access", matching the onboarding
  wording.</li>
          </ul>
      ]]></description>
